Configuration

Pass in the workingdir as J:/ElectSolve/Blue/Rcode, or where the directory is located. This can be done from the r script which creates the report.

Depending on the install location for the mark down file (.Rmd) the working directoty should be something similar to setwd(J:/ElectSolve/Blue/Rcode).

Query

                SELECT 
                   ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY ReadDate) AS RowID
                  ,[ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads].[MeterIdentifier] as 'Meter ID'
                  ,[ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads].[ReadDate] as 'Read Date/Time'
                  ,[ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads].[ReadValue] as 'Voltage'
                  ,[ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads].[LocationNumber] as 'Location ID'
                    ,[MDM].[dbo].[Substation].[SubstationName] as 'Substation'
                FROM [ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads]
                join [MDM].[dbo].[Location]
                on [ODMReporting].[ODM].[IntervalReads].LocationNumber = [MDM].[dbo].[Location].LocationNumber
                join [MDM].[dbo].[Substation]
                on [MDM].[dbo].[Location].SubstationId = [MDM].[dbo].[Substation].SubstationId
                where MeterIdentifier = '200420' 
                and (UOM = 'Voltage')
                and (ReadQualityCode = 3)
                and (ReadDate > '2016-01-01' AND ReadDate <= '2017-01-01')
                order by MeterIdentifier asc, ReadDate asc
